Pre-Game Insights: Steph Curry was listed as available despite a right hip contusion, and Coach Steve Kerr discussed plans for team rotation.
Curry emphasized the importance of team commitment and high energy over individual egos.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played at the Delta Center in Salt Lake City, Utah, with a 9:30 p.m. EDT tip-off.
The game could be watched on NBCS-BA, KJZZ, NBA League Pass, and Fubo TV.
